---
<section class="py-20 bg-gray-900 text-white">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Découvrez l'Impact de l'Affichage Digital</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-300">
        Voyez comment notre réseau d'affichage dynamique transforme l'expérience publicitaire
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="relative max-w-4xl mx-auto aspect-video rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl">
      <iframe
        class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full"
        src="https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/7XEkcLJA8yQ?rel=0"
        title="Digital Signage Promotional Video"
        frameborder="0"
        allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture"
        allowfullscreen
        loading="lazy"
      ></iframe>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mt-16 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="bg-primary/20 w-16 h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 10l4.553-2.276A1 1 0 0121 8.618v6.764a1 1 0 01-1.447.894L15 14M5 18h8a2 2 0 002-2V8a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v8a2 2 0 002 2z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Contenu Dynamique</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-400">Diffusez du contenu interactif et engageant</p>
      </div>

      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="bg-primary/20 w-16 h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Analytics en Temps Réel</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-400">Suivez les performances de vos campagnes</p>
      </div>

      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="bg-primary/20 w-16 h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Large Audience</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-400">Touchez des milliers de spectateurs quotidiennement</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
